        {
            "title": "A股半日跌  PMI數據遜預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日收跌，官方製造業PMI遜預期，消息公布後大市向下，兩市成交合計15566.69億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20190507_FI_A-share_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20190507_FI_A-share_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日跌25點或0.63%，報3961點，今早開報3985點，跌1點，最高3986，與昨天收市價持平，即拾級而下，低見3957，跌29點或0.73%，為上午低位，半日成交6970.91億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日報13447，跌84點或0.62%，今早開報13517點，跌15點或0.11%，中段高見13618，升83點或0.61%，為半日高位，尾段見13447，跌85點或0.63%，半日成交8595.78億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日跌48點或1.02%，報4661，今早開報4702，跌7點或0.14%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創板指數半日跌48點或1.49%，報3214點，今早開報3260，跌3點或0.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地10月官方製造業PMI跌至49，遜市場預期的49.6，上月為49.8。</p>\n</div>",
